{"tid":1397090,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人應該拒絕警察嘅執法權力","createTime":"2019-08-02T10:13:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-02T13:03:23.000Z","uid":167878,"like":23,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f5b3c16c9f171c76298f82f810fb6f404dc57214","tid":1397090,"uid":167878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T10:13:53.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">警察再無資格進行執法角色<br />\n香港市民要拒絕承認警察執法嘅權力<br />\n由香港人代替佢地執行所謂嘅警權</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.taitau.net/power\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.taitau.net%2Fpower&d=7O3ztiABqAoAY%2BrF22wgzXyU4AarvyINc8S1qmu5ZLM%3D&h=ddba6c83\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.taitau.net/power</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人應該令警察執唔到任何法</span></strong><br />\n我地無須再遵從警察任何指令<br />\ncheck身份證 搜身 協助警察調查之類<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">甚至應該阻止警察執法</span></strong><br />\n就算係捉人橫過馬路 隨地扔垃圾<br />\n嗰d人由我地香港市民自己嚟捉<br />\n我咁講亦唔係鼓勵香港人犯法&nbsp;<br />\n而係叫香港人自己取代警察執法<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">因為而家嘅警察永遠企係人民對立面<br />\n多次對香港市民不公平地執法<br />\n又與三合會合作對香港市民進行恐怖襲擊<br />\n其後又用催淚彈 橡膠子彈保護返班黑社會<br />\n又將槍口瞄向頭部 用過期催淚彈<br />\n令示威嘅香港市民造成永久性損傷</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n若果警察想強行執法<br />\n我地視佢地為犯罪分子 需要拘捕"},{"pid":"f20a578b2630c9cd143210f98e1682d0052bb3de","tid":1397090,"uid":167878,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T10:14:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">麻包袋</span></span>"},{"pid":"dd633b109816e953d28932c584afef9232a096ee","tid":1397090,"uid":167878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T10:14:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">麻包袋</span></span>"},{"pid":"f1b6d3ab342a98f3892fbf3f987af4f80571fcb4","tid":1397090,"uid":215861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T10:14:31.000Z","msg":"8月5日一齊罷工啦<br />\n金鐘見！"},{"pid":"229eab